# For more info on HTTP files go to https://aka.ms/vs/httpfile
@host=https://localhost
@port=57679

### Create a new order
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{$guid}}",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Create order with non-existent product (should fail)
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{$guid}}",
  "customerName": "Jane Smith",
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 999,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Create order with invalid quantity (should fail validation)
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{$guid}}",
  "customerName": "Bob Wilson",
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 0
    }
  ]
}